      <title>乌克兰高级顾问称，乌克兰欢迎俄罗斯参加下次峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/ukraine-open-to-see-russia-at-next-summit-zelenskiy-key-aide-yermak-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基的幕僚长表示，乌克兰可能会邀请俄罗斯参加与国际伙伴举行的下一次会议，旨在制定未来和平谈判的方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/ukraine-open-to-see-russia-at-next-summit-zelenskiy-key-aide-yermak-says</guid>
