      <title>台湾抗议者聚集在立法者面前审议有争议的法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/taiwan-braces-for-protests-as-lawmakers-return-to-disputed-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾立法者就一项有争议的法案展开了新一轮辩论，批评人士称该法案旨在遏制新总统赖清德，此举再次引发民众走上街头抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/taiwan-braces-for-protests-as-lawmakers-return-to-disputed-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 02:25:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>李克强访马 中马承诺加强合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/premier-li-visits-malaysia-as-anwar-balances-us-china-interests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强在对马来西亚进行为期三天的访问期间，中马双方承诺深化经贸关系、推进重大项目建设。]]></description>
