      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克领导的保守党将失去英国三分之二的席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/sunak-s-tories-on-course-to-lose-more-than-two-in-three-uk-seats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最新的逐席分析显示，当英国民众下个月进行投票时，里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党将失去在上次大选中赢得的席位的三分之二以上，这意味着首相所在的保守党将在选举中惨败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/sunak-s-tories-on-course-to-lose-more-than-two-in-three-uk-seats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 17:01:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
